vote.title: Authorize the third of three, one-year renewal options, to the master agreement with VetSource Mobility, LLC for ruggedized mobile data computers for the Department of Information and Technology Services - Not to exceed $2,100,460.42 - Financing: Data Service Fund ($2,000,000.00) and Communication Service Fund ($100,460.42) to be reimbursed by June 2023 from Master Lease Equipment Funds ($2,100,460.42)
